Comment: 0,0:22:04.05,0:22:06.22,Scr,,0,0,0,,--------ED「more＜STRONGLY」--------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.65,0:22:20.53,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.15}出逢った　大粒の奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.53,0:22:24.74,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.15}忘れはしないよ　ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.74,0:22:26.91,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.15}色褪せた未来-FUTURE-
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.91,0:22:32.04,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.15}何か変わる…予感がしてた
