Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.52,0:23:01.11,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.15}FACE UP!  STRONGLY
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.11,0:23:06.70,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.15}あなたと超えて行く　地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.70,0:23:13.71,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.15}傷だらけなのは闘った証
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.71,0:23:15.58,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.15}SO, CHANGING THE WORLD
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.58,0:23:23.21,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.15}失った歓び必ず取り戻すから
